originalText.text: Please save yourself a trip from this "gynecologist". Yelena was the worst doctor experience I have ever had. I had terrible pain for months and she was gaslighting me all throughout, saying my symptoms are not real, she prescribed an antibiotic without seeing any test results (which going to another doctor I found out I had a yeast infection and antibiotics obviously make it 10 times worse). Her only solution was ibuprofen and when I said there must be a root reason because I am in so much pain her response was "take 5 ibuprofens a day".  What a waste of a person! Not to mention you have to wait to see her at least an hour or longer even if you have an appointment. People working front desk though are amazing, they made the experience a bit better.
